    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:16">The map feature in Plot-It allows users to view the geographical information of the
        events found in the timeline.</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="taskbody:1;7:15">
