            <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="step:1;9:19">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="cmd:1;10:22">Click on the map. Users can move the map around using either their cursor
                    or the navigation button located in the top left corner of the map. </cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="info:1;12:23">
                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="p:1;13:24">Users can zoom the map two ways. The first is using your mouse, you can
                        scroll in and out of the map using smart features of your mouse. The second
                        is using the existing zoom tools located on the left side of the map. <image placement="break" href="https://cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A6008e2b4-da37-4959-941e-b62dfd71879c/datastream/OBJ/view" id="image_o2l_lvq_5r" align="center" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="image:1;18:67"/></p>
                </info>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="step:2;21:19">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="cmd:2;22:22">Play around with the map, selecting a satellite view of the map or making the
                    map bigger using the small black arrow at the bottom of the map.</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Users/ilovan/CWRC%20Documentation%20-%20everything/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="info:2;24:23">
